 So, and in fact, if you do that,

1:13:26.380 --> 1:13:28.380
 when I started doing this,

1:13:28.380 --> 1:13:30.100
 and it helped me lose weight,

1:13:30.100 --> 1:13:31.700
 is that I'm exposing myself

1:13:31.700 --> 1:13:34.020
 to the right amount of light, dark cycle.

1:13:34.020 --> 1:13:35.940
 I'm eating at regular time.

1:13:35.940 --> 1:13:37.020
 It is amazing.

