 but also to light.

1:14:02.300 --> 1:14:03.140
 Exactly.

1:14:03.140 --> 1:14:04.540
 And you know, in the wild,

1:14:04.540 --> 1:14:06.420
 you could imagine why energy level

1:14:06.420 --> 1:14:08.420
 through the arcuate nucleus-

